scenes.description: The group shares their experiences of living in or visiting Japan, covering topics like trains, signage, and polite delivery services.
Takanashi Kiara introduces a quiz game called "Queen of Japanese Etiquette" to learn more about Japanese culture.
The first theme of the game is "Daily Life". Question 1 is about the custom of taking off shoes indoors in Japan.
Question 2 of "Daily Life" covers "Aizuchi" or interjecting during a conversation to show you are listening.
